name: Sunset
description: Sunset, the swiss army knife of Discord Bots
changelog: -Fixed an issue where the ban command would not work
-Fixed an issue where the bot would crash when a role changed due to the litemode.txt file not existing
-Fixed an issue where DM commands would not work due to the bot trying to call the API for Guild IDs (DMs don't have these so it makes sense)
-Fixed an issue where some parts of the `serversettings` command would not work
-Added the ability to disable server announcements from Sunset in `serversettings` command
